<h2>🎉 Your Property is Now Live!</h2>

<p>Hello {{firstName}},</p>

<p>Exciting news! Your property listing is now <strong>live</strong> on Immobilier.ch and is visible to thousands of potential buyers and renters.</p>

<div class="success-box">
  <p><strong>🚀 Your property is now published!</strong></p>
</div>

<div class="property-card">
  <h3>{{propertyTitle}}</h3>
  <p class="address">📍 {{propertyAddress}}</p>
  <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-weight: 600; color: #1a73e8;">
    {{formatCurrency propertyPrice "CHF"}} {{#if isRent}}/ month{{/if}}
  </p>
</div>

<p><strong>Tips to get more visibility:</strong></p>
<ul style="padding-left: 20px; line-height: 2;">
  <li>📸 Add high-quality photos of your property</li>
  <li>📝 Write a detailed and engaging description</li>
  <li>💰 Keep your pricing competitive</li>
  <li>⏱️ Respond quickly to inquiries</li>
</ul>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
  <a href="{{propertyUrl}}" class="btn-primary">View Your Live Listing</a>
  <br><br>
  <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="btn-secondary">Manage in Dashboard</a>
</div>

<p>We'll notify you when potential buyers or renters show interest in your property.</p>

<p>Good luck with your listing!<br><strong>The Immobilier.ch Team</strong></p>
